  <abstract>Image of two young boys and a young girl seated on concrete steps outside a building.  A cat walks in front of them.  They girl is holding a slate or book and drawing on it while the two boys look over her shoulder.  Annotation on reverse reads: "The children of Greece need medical care immediately to enable them to grow into healthy useful citizens of tomorrow.  Here two little Greek boys get their first lesson in writing from their older sister.  To send medical aid and hospital supplies to the people of Greece the Canadian Relief to Greece Appeal is asking the people of Canada for $1,500,000."</abstract>
